  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a small pot over medium heat.",
    "Place sweetcorn kernels in a colander and blanch in boiling water for 3 minutes, then drain and rinse with cold water.",
    "In the pot, heat olive oil over medium heat. Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and diced carrot, sauté for 2 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Stir in ground cumin, coriander, cinnamon, ginger, and cayenne pepper; cook for 30 seconds to toast the spices.",
    "Pour in low-sodium vegetable broth and water, bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add blanched sweetcorn kernels to the pot, simmer for 5 minutes so the flavors meld.",
    "Using an immersion blender, blend the soup until smooth and velvety; alternatively, transfer in batches to a countertop blender.",
    "Stir in lemon juice, season with a pinch of salt if needed (keeping it low-sodium), and heat through.",
    "Ladle into bowls and garnish with chopped cilantro or parsley."
  ],
